parameters.pythonCode:
# Node 11: Extract Email Info
# Description: Extrait restaurantEmail et restaurantEmailCC pour chaque facture

# R√©cup√©rer les donn√©es de la facture courante
current_item = items[0]['json']

# Extraire les informations email
restaurant_email = current_item.get('restaurantEmail', '')
restaurant_email_cc = current_item.get('restaurantEmailCC', '')
restaurant_nom = current_item.get('restaurantNom', 'Restaurant')

# Validation: Si pas d'email, utiliser fallback ou skip
if not restaurant_email or restaurant_email.strip() == '':
    # Option 1: Fallback email (DEV)
    restaurant_email = 'etienne.broca@icloud.com'
    
    # Option 2: Skip cette facture (PROD - √† activer plus tard)
    # return []  # Retourne rien = skip cette it√©ration

# Nettoyer le CC (peut √™tre vide)
if restaurant_email_cc and restaurant_email_cc.strip() != '':
    restaurant_email_cc = restaurant_email_cc.strip()
else:
    restaurant_email_cc = None  # None = pas de CC

# Log pour debugging
print(f"üìß Email mapping - Restaurant: {restaurant_nom}")
print(f"   To: {restaurant_email}")
if restaurant_email_cc:
    print(f"   CC: {restaurant_email_cc}")

# Retourner les donn√©es enrichies
return [{
    'json': {
        **current_item,  # Garde toutes les donn√©es existantes
        'emailTo': restaurant_email,  # Email nettoy√©
        'emailCC': restaurant_email_cc,  # CC nettoy√© (ou None)
        'hasCC': restaurant_email_cc is not None  # Flag pour condition
    }
}]
